snippet.title: Kimmel Got Canceled (And Nobody Cares) (Official Satire Music Video)
snippet.description:
They finally came for Kimmel... in this song, at least! 

What happens when the canceller becomes the cancelled? We fired up the AI and created this satirical banger imagining the woke mob finally turning on the late-night king himself, Jimmy Kimmel. From old clips to new apologies, no one is safe in the hilarious spiral of modern outrage culture! 

Is this song a bop or a flop? Is cancel culture coming for EVERYONE? Let us know what you think in the comments below! 

If you enjoyed this parody, please SMASH that LIKE button, SHARE with a friend who needs a laugh, and SUBSCRIBE for more comedy that dares to go there!
